{"tid":1314022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句「維護緊不義政權」 中五生遭警員大陣仗包圍截查","createTime":"2019-07-14T04:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:28.000Z","uid":273587,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90e21bedf5f86d3ad98f40b65eaf72a817171e2f","tid":1314022,"uid":273587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:06:45.000Z","msg":"各位小心d 宜㗎講句野就比人圍<br />\n就算你係講緊個真相出黎<br />\n<br />\n事發經過:<br />\n晚上9時45分，家住上水的中五沈同學，約了朋友在區內吃飯，當時他推着單車準備由龍運街橫過新運路，其間他向多名迎面走來的警員說：「如果政權係不義，你哋就維護緊一個不義嘅政權。」<br />\n<br />\n他稱，當時警員大為激動，其中一人推撞胸口，並粗暴地將他推去行人路，他當場眼鏡飛脫，連人帶單車失平衡跌倒地上。其後多名手持盾牌的防暴警察更將他包圍，向他索取身份證查閱，又登記地址盤問。<br />\n<br />\n其間，更有警員手持攝錄機拍攝，他向警員解釋：「我只係講如果政府不公義，你哋就維護緊一個不義嘅政權，唔明白點解會觸怒到你哋？」警員繼續向他查問數分鐘，才將他放行。<br />\n<br />\n事件中，沈同學右膝擦傷，他接受訪問講述事發經過，他指不明白講句説話亦被當成罪犯，竟要警方錄影查證。他指自己下午沒有參予遊行，事發時只是路經示威地帶，所說亦是有感而發，覺得警方行為匪夷所思，「只係講一句嘢，又冇冒犯性、冇攻擊性，唔明會有咁大反應，完全唔明白」。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190713/59820957?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190713%2F59820957%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPapUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b74f862a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190713%2F59820957%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a4ec760e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190713/59820957?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"95c8f03f1d074a620cfb5a5509684af7d837c279","tid":1314022,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"全部同我入黎！教你下一步點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"51aae50ea353adc1d0bca08efc199120700f35bd","tid":1314022,"uid":265256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:16:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"449e862f5f7deeb723916ab2168a952cb207959c","tid":1314022,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:20:40.000Z","msg":"因為講中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf6678f2e2cfef6761b4163e8d1f95c8b4eac08","tid":1314022,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:23:08.000Z","msg":"心虛，用憤怒黎掩飾"},{"pid":"3446d2748d53eef0471be3770615ce5d742dcd5d","tid":1314022,"uid":41428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"on99 黑警"},{"pid":"03e1639e5b623d14b40667b68a9138bb6bcc1d79","tid":1314022,"uid":137506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:26:28.000Z","msg":"心虛所以用暴力嚟掩飾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e102303c06b74b0766a079ddc40d848de62ccb57","tid":1314022,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:30:28.000Z","msg":"推!"}]}